des:
Twenty One Hot Carribbean Vacations is a skill to help you discover some great places to vacation in the a Carribbean. Nothing says vacation like crystalline blue waters, white-sand beaches and luxurious indulgence. That's why we're counting down the 21 best destinations in the Caribbean, where vacation is a lifestyle.

You can say:

"Alexa, open Twenty One Carribbean Vacations"
"Alexa, start Twenty One Carribbean Vacations"
"Alexa, launch Twenty One Carribbean Vacations"
